Celebrity Big Brother 1 Australia

Celebrity Big Brother 1 Australia aired in 2002 and ran from 7-21-02 to 8-12-02 for duration of 23 days. It benefited the Ronald McDonald House and The Starlight Foundation. Now for the bad. The video in this series is not very good. Series 1 and 2 as well as this celeb version all have a few video issues but this series is the worst of the three. I have searched everywhere for a different copy of this series and have never
